      <body>
         <div type="translation">
            <ab>Year 20 of Imperator Caesar Titus Aelius Hadrianus Antoninus Augustus Pius. Work done on the dike works for year 20, Payni 25-29, at the canal of Hermoithes, on behalf of Tebtunis, (2nd h.) Soterichos, son of Ptollion the son of Theon, his mother being Didy(). (3rd h.) I, Marcus, have signed it.</ab>
